# NewsGen AI Environment Variables

# ==========================================
# AI PROVIDERS (Configure at least one)
# ==========================================

# OPTION 1: Google Gemini (FREE - RECOMMENDED)
# Get your key: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# Free tier: 15 requests/min, 1M requests/day
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# OPTION 2: Groq (FREE - Fast inference)
# Get your key: https://console.groq.com/keys
# Free tier with rate limits
# VITE_GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# OPTION 3: OpenAI (PAID - Fallback)
# Get your key: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Uses gpt-4o-mini model (~$0.15 per 1M tokens)
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# ==========================================
# NEWS API (Currently using Make.com webhook)
# ==========================================

# Optional: Direct NewsAPI.org integration
# Get your key: https://newsapi.org/register
# Free tier: 100 requests/day, $9/mo for 100K requests
# VITE_NEWS_API_KEY=your_news_api_key_here

# ==========================================
# NOTES
# ==========================================
# - App will try providers in order: Gemini → Groq → OpenAI
# - Only configure the providers you want to use
# - Gemini is recommended for best free tier
# - Remove comment (#) to enable optional variables
